English.Text: A buccaneer's hoard! The detonation goes off with a pleasing muffled thud, thanks to the care taken in the packing of the bomb. "Ha-ha!" the captain rasps with glee, "pirate kings be damned!" Through the fissure made by the dynamite comes a first glimpse of the sarcophagus' sensational gilded interior, and the many riches within!
